Revision history for Perl extension Lingua::Num2Word.

0.07    2004-06-21
        - documentation update

0.06    2004-06-17
        - added informations about supported range (to be verified)
        - fix returned russian string for '0' (cut off currency)
        - Changelog update (added release date)
        - use q§...§ for templates to be more readable instead of
          mixing interpolation and concatenation
        - add support for new language/package
          no - Lingua::NO::Num2Word

0.05    2004-06-10
        - langs() and known_langs() return value depends on calling context

0.04    2004-06-10
        - update docs
        - output is in utf8 from now
        - add support for languages/packages
          it - Lingua::IT::Numbers
          nl - Lingua::NL::Numbers
          pl - Lingua::PL::Numbers
          ru - Lingua::RU::Number
          sv - Lingua::SV::Num2Word
          zh - Lingua::ZH::Numbers

0.03    2002-12-18
        - add support for language
          eu - Lingua::EU::Numbers

0.02    2002-07-16
        - fix procedural interface (thanks to Briac Pilpré)

0.01    2002-07-15
        - original version; spuport for languages/packages:
	  af - Lingua::AF::Numbers
	  cs - Lingua::CS::Num2Word
	  de - Lingua::DE::Num2Word
	  en - Lingua::EN::Numbers
	  es - Lingua::ES::Numeros
	  fr - Lingua::FR::Numbers
	  id - Lingua::ID::Nums2Words
	  ja - Lingua::JA::Number
	  pt - Lingua::PT::Nums2Words
